- "Sown the most seeds" refers to the highest number of data sharing agreements and publications;
- "Shots" refers to the total shoot length from the experiments associated with these researchers.

sql:
SELECT plant_id, date, shoot_length
FROM plant_growth
ORDER BY date DESC;

